I uploaded a paper to the files section of this group. Its an overview of
what is known about modularity in strictly evolutionary (i.e. not
developmental) systems. I wrote it as a midterm paper, so its a little
rough still, but Ken thought some of you might be interested in it. If you
get a chance to read it, let me know what you think.
